name: Sample Pack
description:
A bundle of goodies sure to impress! This sample pack overflows with colorful invitations, whimsical note cards, gorgeous stationery and much more. Once these samples land in your hand, I'm certain you'll want a set of your own.

Each sample card labeled with printing style, type and weight of paper stock.

Price will be credited to your first custom order.

name: Quotation Block Giclee Print
description:
This timeless and poignant quote by Forest E. Witcraft is the perfect tribute to a parent, grandparent, teacher (end-of-the-year gift), caregiver, or beloved friend.

This archival giclée print - also known as watercolor giclée - is beautifully printed in the U.S. with the highest-quality archival inks on heavy, fine art paper finished with subtle texture. Gorgeous and refined.

- Choose from chocolate/blue (shown) OR chocolate/pink. 

- Print size is 8.5" x 10.5." Fits nicely in an 8x10 frame. Please note that frame and matte are not included.
